{"tid":1236602,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"希望成立「文宣台」以助對抗長輩圖及增加國際影響力","createTime":"2019-06-17T12:49:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T12:30:09.000Z","uid":52090,"like":308,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"5ab70e24bbcfd85f83a7840e90d461d01fcfa5e0","tid":1236602,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:49:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> 今後議題 - 文宣組常態化 &amp; 71要求政改 &amp; 2020年9月立法會選戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1232620/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1232620/page/1</a> </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n由5月尾，6月頭開始，不少巴打絲打為救香港，<br />\n自行設計多個懶人包，長輩圖，收集及翻譯資料給國際傳媒及政府<br />\n對本土對國際影響力超出預期，再配合和平及勇武示威活動，<br />\n為香港創造出新𥌓光！<br />\n<br />\n由此可看，「文宣」工作對香港影響深遠，<br />\n而上方文章總結了13種「文宣」工作，<br />\n及常規化，持續性「文宣」的好處<br />\n<br />\n因此，希望連仔可以建立一個新台「文宣台」<br />\n讓大量「文宣」POST可以集中在一個地方<br />\n同時希望新的「文宣台」POST可以依舊在「時事台」顯示<br />\n（類似吹水台可以睇到所有台的POST）<br />\n以取得一眾時事台巴絲打的關注<br />\n<br />\n反送中一戰，我地未鸁，<br />\n「文宣台」對我地勝敗有關鍵作用，<br />\n希望連仔可以幫我地香港人，打鸁佢！！！"},{"pid":"6e71c1c0287f34b4cada20a211314dd9eeda8b4a","tid":1236602,"uid":35592,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:50:08.000Z","msg":"岩岩收到呢張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來係驚天大陰謀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5hdeVNU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5hdeVNU.png&h=e6ed2119&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f2b008588b7cfd5e94c13cdfddefe13532af053","tid":1236602,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:51:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e1ac1c40bfa5dac4452f0f06b53d78b676c9bc4","tid":1236602,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:57:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1478775254e3c4d6